                <h3>S-N curve (Basquin, log-log) · cycles to failure</h3>
                <svg id="fa_sn" class="mz-svg" viewBox="0 0 760 240" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"></svg>
                <div class="mz-note">Basquin: sigma_ar = a&middot;N^b with a, b fitted through (1000 cycles, 0.9&middot;Sut) and (1e6 cycles, Se). Life is read from the equivalent fully-reversed stress sigma_ar.</div>
              </div>
